{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_守夜坐下",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·守夜·都是可怜人（Axiu情感锚点）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "wrap_守夜",
              "state": "done",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "after_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "after_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "坐过了。后半夜冷，话也说完了。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他在供桌边的草垫上坐下来。庙里很静，静得能听见灯芯吃油的细响。",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（无名无姓，停在这儿。要不是庙里出钱，连口薄棺都没有。）",
      "next": "n3"
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（俺从小没爹没娘，要是哪天横死在外头……估摸也就这待遇。）——都是可怜人。",
      "next": "n_cue"
    },
    "n_cue": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_守夜坐下",
            "signal": "shouye_lamp_steady"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n4"
    },
    "n4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "说不上来从哪一刻起，灯苗不晃了。火光稳稳的，把灵前照得很安生——一缕似有似无的香粉味，陪他坐了后半夜。",
      "next": "n5"
    },
    "n5": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "那半夜，什么都没出。天蒙蒙亮时，他给那具无名女尸上了三炷香——自掏的香火钱。",
      "next": "n_sig"
    },
    "n_sig": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_守夜坐下",
            "signal": "shouye_sit_done"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n6"
    },
    "n6": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "守夜钱二十文，庙祝一文没少给。出庙的时候，他回头看了一眼那盏灯——还亮着。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}